WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 12=

01:38.864 --> 01:43.024
But before they reached the capital,
the late emperor passed away.

01:44.543 --> 01:46.864
You should know about it as well.

01:49.424 --> 01:53.263
I heard that they wanted
to take him away and crown him emperor.

01:55.424 --> 02:00.383
Do you really think a dozen or so people
could install a new emperor?

02:19.304 --> 02:21.824
You abducted the crown prince's son.

02:22.544 --> 02:25.183
You're all ill-disposed,
and your crime is punishable by death.

02:25.424 --> 02:26.663
Seize them!

02:27.343 --> 02:29.623
(The fire in the Eastern Palace
was suspicious.)

02:30.544 --> 02:32.824
(Mo Jingli, as the sole son
of the late crown prince,)

02:32.880 --> 02:34.992
(would face danger
upon returning to the capital.)

02:35.104 --> 02:36.984
(With his consent, they decided)

02:36.984 --> 02:40.144
(to send him to Duke Hua's barracks
for temporary shelter.)

02:40.463 --> 02:44.264
(However, Marquis Muyang bent the truth
and intercepted them halfway.)

02:44.264 --> 02:47.183
(He then falsely charged them
with abducting Mo Jingli and rebellion.)

02:57.943 --> 03:01.623
I remember many officials doubted it
at that time.

03:01.984 --> 03:04.304
Duke Hua took the lead
in speaking up for them.

03:04.663 --> 03:07.063
Yes, many had doubts.

03:07.743 --> 03:10.024
Marquis Muyang
couldn't fully convict them.

03:10.463 --> 03:12.384
He could only imprison them.

03:14.223 --> 03:15.824
But when things were at a stalemate,

03:16.704 --> 03:20.183
Mo Jingli suddenly came forward
and identified them.

03:23.024 --> 03:24.704
He was only 14 at the time.

03:26.183 --> 03:30.104
He was so young,
and I understand he was afraid.

03:31.384 --> 03:32.424
(Testimony)
I can also

03:32.824 --> 03:35.424
imagine the methods
Marquis Muyang would use to coerce him.

03:36.984 --> 03:38.264
But I cannot forgive.

03:40.544 --> 03:42.984
(Mo Jingli)
Those disciples all died that year.

03:44.503 --> 03:46.503
The oldest among them was 24,

03:47.743 --> 03:49.584
(Mo Jingli)
and the youngest was only 12.

03:56.223 --> 03:57.864
Why are you suddenly telling me this?

04:01.183 --> 04:02.704
I just want to tell you

04:03.623 --> 04:05.663
that there is nothing
between Mo Jingli and me.

04:06.063 --> 04:09.824
Even if he hadn't ended the engagement,
I would never have married him.

04:20.064 --> 04:22.103
There were many snakes
at the bottom of the cliff,

04:23.144 --> 04:24.504
as thick as a bowl mouth.

04:25.584 --> 04:28.704
They kept circling me,
and no matter what, they wouldn't leave.

04:31.543 --> 04:33.223
I knew you would come to save me.

04:33.744 --> 04:35.303
So I kept dealing with them.

04:37.384 --> 04:38.903
But I got bitten.

04:39.944 --> 04:41.223
I passed out.

04:50.863 --> 04:51.704
I'm sorry.

04:53.663 --> 04:56.343
It's not your fault.
You couldn't help it.

04:57.384 --> 05:00.384
Your Highness,
may I ask you for one thing?

05:01.744 --> 05:02.543
What is it?

05:06.103 --> 05:07.783
I want to help treat your leg injury.

05:08.184 --> 05:09.584
Will you let me try?

05:18.423 --> 05:19.983
Your Highness, just do it for my sake.

05:21.303 --> 05:23.144
You and I met in the desert back then.

05:23.543 --> 05:24.944
How brave and mighty you were.

05:25.663 --> 05:28.903
Now, because of this injury,
you are confined to this chair

05:29.223 --> 05:31.343
and powerless to fight back
against those evil people.

05:31.624 --> 05:32.863
I don't want you like that.

05:34.944 --> 05:36.463
You can consider me vain

05:37.824 --> 05:39.103
or worldly.

05:39.704 --> 05:40.983
Anyway, in my heart,

05:42.504 --> 05:45.103
Your Highness is an indomitable hero.

05:45.504 --> 05:49.103
I cannot bear, nor can I stand by
and watch you give up on yourself.

05:51.584 --> 05:52.663
It can't be cured.

05:52.824 --> 05:53.624
It can be cured.

05:54.663 --> 05:55.944
Your Highness, let me try.

05:56.223 --> 05:58.103
I promise it will definitely be cured.

06:03.663 --> 06:07.264
Please, just let me give it a try.

06:26.096 --> 06:27.600
(Upright and Principled)

06:43.423 --> 06:44.144
Who's there?

06:45.303 --> 06:46.184
Who's outside?

07:04.223 --> 07:05.024
Go away.

07:21.264 --> 07:22.736
(A heartless man is terrified at night,
with a ghost hanging from the beam)

08:02.303 --> 08:03.103
Your Highness.

08:04.264 --> 08:05.744
This soup helps you sober up.

08:05.824 --> 08:07.584
After you finish the soup,
go to bed early.

08:13.584 --> 08:15.944
Your Highness,
please don't drink anymore.

08:33.744 --> 08:34.984
Your Highness, be careful.

08:42.344 --> 08:44.144
Your Highness, what are you doing?

08:48.063 --> 08:48.943
Your Highness.

08:50.384 --> 08:53.744
Your Highness, please go inside quickly.
It's raining too hard outside.

08:54.104 --> 08:56.583
Leave me alone. I'm not going back.

08:57.384 --> 08:59.303
If Mo Jingli doesn't come,
I won't go inside.

08:59.303 --> 09:01.144
Your Highness, you...

09:02.423 --> 09:03.744
I'll go find His Highness now.

09:44.144 --> 09:46.864
Mo Jingli, I hate you.

10:10.943 --> 10:12.543
My mom is right.

10:13.384 --> 10:15.344
The men in the capital are all bad.

10:16.224 --> 10:18.464
They seem good yet bad inside.

10:41.104 --> 10:44.104
Ling'er went to prepare your medicine.

10:44.783 --> 10:45.703
I won't take it.

10:47.703 --> 10:49.144
I don't even want to live anymore.

10:49.583 --> 10:51.104
Why should I still take medicine?

10:53.943 --> 10:54.744
Stop right there.

10:57.224 --> 10:58.183
Do not leave.

10:59.464 --> 11:00.864
Let's put it all on the table.

11:01.144 --> 11:02.943
How could you treat me like this?

11:05.703 --> 11:07.943
You can write a few poems,
so you think you're great?

11:08.423 --> 11:10.104
You can compose, but so what?

11:12.264 --> 11:13.063
Careful.

11:13.303 --> 11:14.183
Don't touch me.

11:18.024 --> 11:19.264
When I was at home,

11:20.583 --> 11:22.104
I was loved by my family.

11:24.024 --> 11:25.943
My mom doted on me.

11:28.024 --> 11:30.303
My father also favored me.

11:32.943 --> 11:37.104
Even Ye Li, as prominent as she was,
couldn't bully me.

11:40.224 --> 11:43.303
So why did I end up like this
after getting married?

11:48.663 --> 11:50.984
I looked forward to marrying you.

11:53.663 --> 11:56.703
You are a man.

11:58.303 --> 12:00.943
If you don't like a woman,
don't marry her.

12:02.344 --> 12:05.984
If you marry her,
you should treat her well.

12:21.464 --> 12:25.543
On our wedding day,
I was originally very happy.

12:28.624 --> 12:30.543
But my happiness lasted only one day.

12:39.303 --> 12:40.543
I hate you.

13:22.384 --> 13:23.624
(I hate you.)

13:24.823 --> 13:26.504
(You really haven't changed one bit.)

13:27.823 --> 13:28.624
Prince Li.

13:29.823 --> 13:31.264
When you say these words,

13:32.384 --> 13:33.943
don't you find yourself ridiculous?

13:34.703 --> 13:36.543
(They all died because of you.)

13:37.344 --> 13:39.224
(I am one of Lishan Academy.)

13:41.144 --> 13:42.703
(I can never forgive you.)

13:43.264 --> 13:46.543
(You should be glad
you broke off our engagement.)

13:48.303 --> 13:51.423
(Otherwise, I might lose control
and kill you on our wedding day.)

13:53.183 --> 13:54.104
(You hate me.)

13:55.264 --> 13:56.423
(You detest me.)

13:57.344 --> 13:58.903
(You think I wanted things this way?)

13:59.864 --> 14:01.104
(I detest myself too.)

14:01.543 --> 14:02.224
Your Highness.

14:07.903 --> 14:09.144
Your Highness, don't be sad.

14:09.823 --> 14:13.264
Lady Ye Li is surely angry
about what happened back then.

14:14.264 --> 14:15.903
She didn't know your situation before.

14:17.104 --> 14:18.703
One day, when she finds out,

14:19.423 --> 14:20.744
she'll definitely understand you.

14:24.464 --> 14:25.224
Really?

14:26.663 --> 14:27.864
Will she?

14:28.744 --> 14:29.583
She will.

14:34.624 --> 14:35.224
Right.

14:36.663 --> 14:37.783
Li will understand.

14:38.344 --> 14:39.783
She has always understood me best.

14:43.303 --> 14:44.344
Caught it?

14:45.024 --> 14:46.783
Caught it. Look.

14:48.224 --> 14:50.464
Probably because I was the son
of the crown prince,

14:50.864 --> 14:52.423
during those years in the academy,

14:52.703 --> 14:56.183
everyone was absolutely polite to me
but kind of distant from me.

14:57.423 --> 14:58.264
Only Li

14:59.104 --> 15:01.663
was like the first ray of sunlight
breaking through the clouds,

15:02.063 --> 15:03.543
pure and ardent.

15:04.583 --> 15:08.903
In that moment,
I realized light actually has warmth.

15:09.744 --> 15:11.303
We were inseparable all day long.

15:11.703 --> 15:12.703
We played together.

15:13.144 --> 15:15.063
We studied
and learned the guqin together.

15:15.823 --> 15:18.984
She would teach me everything
she learned from the tutors.

15:19.703 --> 15:23.384
And every time she left the mountain,
she would buy me many things.

15:23.744 --> 15:28.224
Then later, my grandfather
arranged a marriage for me and Ye Li.

15:30.063 --> 15:34.144
But those most wonderful times
will never come again.

15:35.056 --> 15:35.696
(Lishan Academy)

15:35.696 --> 15:36.943
(The Fourteenth Year of the Jinghe Era)

15:36.943 --> 15:41.183
In the 14th year of the Jinghe era,
dire news came from the capital.

15:42.063 --> 15:43.104
My grandfather was ill.

15:44.823 --> 15:46.543
So I hurried back to the capital.

15:47.063 --> 15:51.224
By the time I arrived at the palace,
my grandfather had already passed away.

15:53.943 --> 15:55.984
The Eastern Palace,
which was once at its zenith,

15:56.543 --> 15:58.984
was also burned to scorched ruins
in a great fire.

16:00.984 --> 16:05.583
The past glory felt like a dream.

16:06.384 --> 16:09.224
Upon waking, I found all traces gone.

16:09.823 --> 16:12.783
Only the faction of Guo Jin
held overwhelming power.

16:13.504 --> 16:18.183
As the son of the late crown prince,
I was confined.

16:19.264 --> 16:22.663
From then on, I never saw Li again.

16:23.504 --> 16:25.783
(First Year of the Xide Era)
Soon after, Mo Xiuwen was in trouble.

16:26.024 --> 16:28.543
Guo Jin's ambition to ascend the throne
was abundantly clear.

16:29.104 --> 16:32.624
Yet she failed because Lishan was shut,
and court officials opposed it.

16:33.744 --> 16:35.903
She stayed calm and changed her mind.

16:36.183 --> 16:38.984
- She placed Mo Yanqi on the throne.
- Bow!

16:39.984 --> 16:41.943
- Long live the emperor!
- Long live the emperor!

16:42.142 --> 16:45.357
(Jingsi Palace)

17:01.344 --> 17:03.224
Three years
after Mo Yanqi ascended the throne,

17:03.703 --> 17:05.623
I finally walked out of Jingsi Palace.

17:06.264 --> 17:08.583
I became a decorative prop
to showcase her benevolence.

17:09.863 --> 17:10.664
I was lucky.

17:10.800 --> 17:11.464
Your Highness.

17:11.464 --> 17:12.543
I survived.

17:23.904 --> 17:25.543
My grandfather is dead.

17:26.143 --> 17:27.383
My father is dead.

17:27.823 --> 17:31.744
Even those brothers I hated
are all dead.

17:32.904 --> 17:34.343
Only I survived.

17:36.024 --> 17:37.904
I'm the emblem of her benevolence.

17:38.464 --> 17:40.543
I am the pet of this imperial city,

17:40.863 --> 17:42.623
the laughingstock of the capital.

17:43.143 --> 17:45.623
Whatever she wants to hear,
I'll say it to her.

17:46.343 --> 17:48.543
Whatever she wants to see,
I'll do it for her.

17:49.343 --> 17:50.623
Dignity means nothing to me.

17:51.264 --> 17:54.264
As long as I'm alive,
I still have a chance.

17:54.704 --> 17:57.863
As long as I'm alive,
I can still see Li again.

17:58.944 --> 18:01.543
But things didn't go as I wished.

18:03.823 --> 18:04.904
What?

18:05.103 --> 18:07.904
You cannot marry Lady Ye Li.

18:10.264 --> 18:11.224
How dare you!

18:11.224 --> 18:13.224
You've finally
gained the Empress Dowager's trust.

18:13.343 --> 18:15.184
You should draw a clear line
with Lishan.

18:15.424 --> 18:17.823
You cannot marry her.

18:17.823 --> 18:18.343
How dare you!

18:18.343 --> 18:20.543
Have you forgotten the fire
in the Eastern Palace?

18:20.543 --> 18:22.303
Won't you avenge your father?

18:22.303 --> 18:23.664
Your Highness.

18:23.863 --> 18:27.543
Even if you don't consider yourself,
think of Lady Ye Li.

18:27.823 --> 18:28.863
Though her days

18:29.264 --> 18:32.623
are hard, she is not in mortal danger.

18:32.664 --> 18:35.184
If you successfully ascend the throne,
it's the best.

18:35.744 --> 18:37.863
But if you fail,
you'll be doomed, Your Highness.

18:38.184 --> 18:39.744
Why drag her down with you?

18:40.583 --> 18:44.264
Once Your Highness successfully
ascends the throne in the future,

18:44.343 --> 18:47.264
you can then marry her
and crown her as the Empress.

18:47.264 --> 18:48.383
Wouldn't that be better?

18:52.224 --> 18:54.904
But I never expected

18:55.543 --> 18:59.143
that Guo Jin would actually betroth Li
to Prince Ding.

19:03.184 --> 19:03.984
Your Highness.

19:06.063 --> 19:06.863
Your Highness.

19:08.863 --> 19:10.224
Time to drink the nuptial wine.

19:37.944 --> 19:40.904
My life has been full of misfortunes.

19:41.783 --> 19:44.224
I've never been able to get what I want.

19:45.744 --> 19:47.303
Fate has never been kind to me.

19:48.024 --> 19:49.823
But I refuse to accept such a fate.

19:51.264 --> 19:52.143
Prince Li?

20:01.063 --> 20:01.863
Sit.

20:06.343 --> 20:08.224
You investigated the weaponry case.

20:11.464 --> 20:13.224
Was Marquis Muyang behind it?

20:19.904 --> 20:20.904
Yes.

20:21.863 --> 20:25.984
Marquis Muyang trafficked in weapons.
He is a parasite of the nation.

20:26.984 --> 20:32.383
I will definitely
bring a parasite like him to justice.

20:35.863 --> 20:38.744
You're a good official,
concerned with the nation.

20:40.543 --> 20:44.264
But now is not the time.

21:08.424 --> 21:09.823
Kill all the useless ones.

21:10.383 --> 21:11.184
Yes.

21:19.024 --> 21:21.904
If you want something,
fight for it yourself.

21:22.103 --> 21:25.103
I have no choice but to walk this path.

21:25.224 --> 21:26.664
And I will never regret it.

21:32.984 --> 21:34.103
Only in this way

21:35.184 --> 21:38.863
can I protect myself,
the former followers of my father,

21:39.704 --> 21:41.143
and Li.

21:44.424 --> 21:45.383
Your Highness.

21:46.343 --> 21:47.464
One day,

21:48.264 --> 21:49.984
you will ascend the throne.

21:51.303 --> 21:53.143
You will obtain everything you desire.

21:59.120 --> 22:04.144
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

22:04.704 --> 22:07.543
You want to treat His Highness's legs?

22:07.623 --> 22:08.424
Yes.

22:09.143 --> 22:11.343
His Highness's leg injury is treatable.

22:11.664 --> 22:13.303
It just takes time.

22:14.543 --> 22:17.904
I plan to start with the acupoints,
like Guanyuan, Qihai

22:18.063 --> 22:19.823
(Zusanli)
Zusanli, and other points,

22:19.904 --> 22:22.623
to dissolve the stagnant
and open the meridians with the needles.

22:22.984 --> 22:25.904
After the meridians are opened,
we'll reset the bones.

22:26.944 --> 22:28.783
His Highness's legs have atrophied now.

22:29.383 --> 22:31.704
Your idea is right, indeed.

22:31.904 --> 22:34.184
Removing stagnant blood is easy,

22:34.464 --> 22:38.024
while opening the meridians is hard.
How will you do, Your Highness?

22:46.063 --> 22:47.103
What is this?

22:47.783 --> 22:48.744
Don't be afraid.

22:48.823 --> 22:50.944
This is a long needle,
one of the nine needles.

22:51.704 --> 22:52.823
According to a medical book,

22:52.944 --> 22:55.024
the long needle is sharp and thin.

22:55.024 --> 22:56.208
It can treat chronic pain.

22:56.383 --> 22:59.343
His highness's legs have atrophied
for eight years.

22:59.464 --> 23:01.904
We need this needle
to pierce the Chengshan point

23:01.904 --> 23:02.984
and the Weizhong point.

23:03.543 --> 23:05.984
It can reduce pain in the waist
and strengthen the lower body.

23:09.823 --> 23:11.424
He has stagnant blood in the waist.

23:11.984 --> 23:14.184
I'll then use a silver needle
on the Shenshu point.

23:14.944 --> 23:16.984
This opens the meridians
to circulate blood freely.

23:17.063 --> 23:19.583
The toxins in the legs
will naturally be relieved.

23:19.696 --> 23:25.240
♪Love is not just romance♪

23:25.776 --> 23:30.186
♪They don't get my obsession♪

23:30.768 --> 23:35.120
♪Why do two struggling souls make a vow♪

23:35.120 --> 23:37.904
♪And stake everything♪

23:39.792 --> 23:44.720
♪Hardship makes us sensible♪

23:44.790 --> 23:50.160
♪Even with all these feelings,
we hold back♪

23:50.160 --> 23:53.360
♪To live once more for each other♪

23:54.192 --> 23:59.029
♪To become a better version
of ourselves♪

23:59.760 --> 24:03.472
♪Love has never been just this.
Who knows♪

24:03.952 --> 24:05.392
(Schedule)

24:05.968 --> 24:08.368
♪If the soul comes with thorns♪

24:08.368 --> 24:11.615
♪Embrace to feel♪

24:13.072 --> 24:14.544
(Herbs)

24:15.348 --> 24:19.248
♪Like friends
always standing side by side♪

24:19.248 --> 24:23.024
♪Love is but a beginning,
knowing each other day and night♪

24:23.024 --> 24:28.176
♪On such a long road,
holding hands and never letting go♪

24:29.488 --> 24:33.136
♪Only then do we understand why love♪

24:33.136 --> 24:37.904
♪Means more than one thing♪

24:42.000 --> 24:46.451
♪The little and big things left
in each other's lives♪

24:46.864 --> 24:51.054
♪Along the way,
we've skipped the explanation of love♪

24:51.054 --> 24:53.648
♪Seeing a complete life♪

24:56.103 --> 24:57.343
Go prepare the medicine.

24:58.664 --> 24:59.464
Yes.

24:59.728 --> 25:03.504
♪Love has never been just this.
Who knows♪

25:03.504 --> 25:05.923
♪Nobody acknowledges your persistence♪

25:05.923 --> 25:08.464
♪If the soul comes with thorns♪

25:08.464 --> 25:11.623
Your Highness,
are His Highness's legs almost healed?

25:14.063 --> 25:15.543
There is the most crucial step to go.

25:15.543 --> 25:19.312
♪We always work together like friends♪

25:19.312 --> 25:22.928
♪Love is but a beginning,
knowing each other day and night♪

25:24.688 --> 25:26.896
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

25:29.456 --> 25:32.943
♪Only then do we understand why love♪

25:32.943 --> 25:35.744
♪Means more than one thing♪

25:35.744 --> 25:37.343
You're reading the official documents?

25:38.383 --> 25:39.984
You're quite busy.

25:40.704 --> 25:42.383
You ban me from going to the office.

25:42.984 --> 25:45.143
So I had no choice
but to bring work home.

25:46.984 --> 25:50.143
The poultice is ready.
I can treat your legs now.

25:53.744 --> 25:57.504
Your leg problem has been delayed long.
It needs to be re-broken and reset.

26:06.464 --> 26:07.823
Breaking bones is very painful.

26:08.024 --> 26:08.823
I know.

26:13.392 --> 26:17.008
♪Love has never been just this,
I hope you know♪

26:18.103 --> 26:19.024
I'm not afraid.

26:19.408 --> 26:21.840
♪We understand when we trade places♪

26:22.664 --> 26:23.744
So confident in me?

26:24.664 --> 26:27.623
Since I let you treat me,
naturally, I trust you.

26:28.664 --> 26:29.783
It's worth a try.

26:30.583 --> 26:32.224
It can't get worse than now.

26:32.592 --> 26:36.432
♪Love is but a beginning,
the pain is brief♪

26:36.432 --> 26:40.383
♪On such a long road,
I hold your fingers♪

26:40.383 --> 26:41.984
I will definitely cure you.

26:42.986 --> 26:53.936
♪I haven't gotten it off my chest♪

26:53.936 --> 26:57.328
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

26:57.328 --> 27:05.904
(Great Ambition and Responsibility)

27:05.904 --> 27:08.823
Two bandits slipped into the capital.

27:09.103 --> 27:11.303
They killed four high-ranking officials.

27:11.783 --> 27:13.984
One of them even died
within the imperial palace.

27:14.224 --> 27:16.424
And Mo Xiuyao's closing report

27:16.904 --> 27:18.623
actually says the bandits are at large.

27:19.424 --> 27:21.184
He only issued a wanted notice.

27:21.424 --> 27:22.863
He is treating all court officials

27:23.224 --> 27:25.264
and me as a fool.

27:25.583 --> 27:27.063
I can't stand this.

27:27.343 --> 27:29.783
Master, don't be mad.

27:30.303 --> 27:34.904
Previously, to catch Yuan Fang,
our men pretended to be bandits.

27:35.383 --> 27:37.424
Mo Xiuyao is just copying us.

27:45.184 --> 27:47.504
We should have eliminated him too.

28:21.184 --> 28:22.264
I've been here for a while.

28:22.984 --> 28:25.863
Your Majesty, what can I do for you?

28:36.744 --> 28:39.704
Mo Xiuyao has gone too far!

28:41.224 --> 28:44.184
Relying on His Majesty's favor,
he's getting bolder.

28:45.704 --> 28:47.704
How did Yuan Fang die?

28:50.543 --> 28:53.103
Your Majesty, I have stressed it before.

28:53.343 --> 28:56.063
I didn't kill Yuan Fang.

28:56.704 --> 28:59.264
All these years,
I've never concealed anything,

28:59.464 --> 29:02.103
small or big, from Your Majesty.

29:03.143 --> 29:06.863
I swear I'm absolutely loyal
to Your Majesty.

29:07.863 --> 29:11.664
Fine, even if I believe your vow,

29:12.504 --> 29:15.504
then why was Yuan Fang captured
in Huaixi?

29:15.783 --> 29:17.680
He was ordered
to investigate the weaponry case.

29:17.863 --> 29:20.704
And your family is based in Huaixi.

29:21.704 --> 29:24.504
Bandits could take him away
from the government office.

29:25.143 --> 29:29.863
Does this matter truly have nothing
to do with your family in Huaixi?

29:30.704 --> 29:32.863
Do you really know nothing at all?

29:33.863 --> 29:34.664
Your Majesty.

29:34.984 --> 29:38.264
Lu Changfu and his men
brought it upon themselves.

29:38.984 --> 29:41.143
I have warned you long ago
to manage your people well.

29:41.863 --> 29:44.224
The emperor values Mo Xiuyao.

29:45.024 --> 29:47.143
Whether he succeeds or fails
is his own thing.

29:47.424 --> 29:50.704
But he cannot fail because of you.
Do you understand?

29:54.623 --> 29:55.424
Your Majesty.

29:56.623 --> 30:00.264
The medicine is ready.
You can drink it now, Your Majesty.

30:05.823 --> 30:07.744
Marquis Muyang, you may leave.

30:21.103 --> 30:23.704
Marquis Muyang,
do you still have something to say?

30:24.024 --> 30:24.823
Your Majesty.

30:26.103 --> 30:29.944
Now you despise me, seeing me

30:30.504 --> 30:31.504
as a worthless thing.

30:32.184 --> 30:33.704
Do you want to cast me aside?

30:34.863 --> 30:36.103
Don't forget.

30:37.103 --> 30:42.264
It was I who did everything I could
for you and eliminated your dissidents.

30:43.383 --> 30:48.343
It was I who supported you consistently.

30:49.424 --> 30:54.744
It was I who crushed the treacherous
and wiped out the villains for you.

30:55.984 --> 30:57.504
Now, the nation is peaceful.

30:59.343 --> 31:01.303
So, you want to discard me

31:02.383 --> 31:03.904
once your purpose is served?

31:04.303 --> 31:05.224
Are you crazy?

31:05.224 --> 31:05.904
Shut up!

31:10.424 --> 31:11.184
What?

31:11.184 --> 31:12.904
You're offending Her Majesty recklessly.

31:13.024 --> 31:14.303
Are you trying to rebel?

31:23.103 --> 31:26.303
Your Majesty,
I'm absolutely loyal to you.

31:26.863 --> 31:29.103
I merely feel aggrieved
and hard to calm.

31:29.623 --> 31:33.464
I beg Your Majesty to discern clearly
and not believe slanderous words.

31:34.904 --> 31:36.343
Otherwise, it will hurt me.

31:46.984 --> 31:50.063
The weather is hot,
and you're a meat-lover.

31:50.264 --> 31:51.303
That makes you irritable.

31:51.744 --> 31:54.143
From now on, be a vegetarian.

32:03.088 --> 32:06.512
(Xiangqi Pavilion)

32:09.224 --> 32:10.063
(Xiangqi Pavilion)
Take care.

32:10.464 --> 32:11.264
Well,

32:11.383 --> 32:13.823
Your Highness, what are we doing here?

32:23.224 --> 32:24.464
My lady, what can I do for you?

32:25.303 --> 32:26.704
I'm here for Lady Yusheng.

32:27.464 --> 32:29.224
Have you come to the wrong place?

32:29.224 --> 32:31.103
Xiangqi Pavilion is a place of pleasure.

32:31.103 --> 32:33.184
It is not a place for ordinary women.

32:33.184 --> 32:36.383
Lady Yusheng and I are old friends.
Just show me the way.

32:39.623 --> 32:40.623
Thank you, my lady.

32:43.424 --> 32:45.823
My lady, here's Lady Yusheng's room.

32:45.944 --> 32:46.744
Thank you.

32:50.664 --> 32:52.863
Wait outside for me.
I'll come out shortly.

32:53.103 --> 32:53.904
Yes.

33:04.504 --> 33:05.623
Your surname is Ye?

33:06.504 --> 33:07.303
Yes.

33:07.783 --> 33:10.704
Lady Ye, have some tea, please.

33:13.704 --> 33:16.823
Lady Ye, how did you get to know Feibai?

33:19.664 --> 33:20.783
How did we meet?

33:21.984 --> 33:23.343
We grew up together.

33:24.424 --> 33:25.623
Childhood sweethearts?

33:30.984 --> 33:32.664
And how did you meet him?

33:33.264 --> 33:36.464
At a banquet on the Shangsi Festival,
I was harassed by a drunkard.

33:36.583 --> 33:38.583
I nearly fell into the lotus pond.

33:38.583 --> 33:40.143
Fortunately, Feibai saved me.

33:41.264 --> 33:43.303
He came under the moonlight.

33:43.583 --> 33:45.823
He alone fought off the drunkard.

33:46.184 --> 33:47.823
Then, with a light flick of his sword,

33:48.184 --> 33:51.904
he retrieved my fallen hairpin
from the pond water.

33:52.504 --> 33:55.063
Afterward, we wandered together
under the moonlight.

33:55.224 --> 33:57.264
We made poems under an old ginkgo tree.

33:58.464 --> 34:01.984
He said, "Do not say autumn frost
hastens the tree's aging."

34:02.704 --> 34:07.303
I continued the verse, "Burn red leaves
to warm the cold washing stone."

34:10.183 --> 34:11.223
What a lovely story.

34:14.223 --> 34:16.824
Lady Ye, what brings you to seek Feibai?

34:22.864 --> 34:24.063
You're finally back.

34:24.063 --> 34:26.183
Why have you been leaving early
and returning late?

34:26.183 --> 34:27.143
I've been busy lately.

34:28.784 --> 34:31.824
Really? Could it be
because of some woman?

34:37.063 --> 34:38.223
This is Princess Ding, Ye Li.

34:38.384 --> 34:40.504
We went to the same academy.

34:40.504 --> 34:41.504
She's married?

34:42.743 --> 34:44.143
Turns out you're Princess Ding.

34:44.904 --> 34:46.223
Please forgive my rudeness.

34:46.984 --> 34:50.663
Yusheng, I need to talk to her alone.

34:51.464 --> 34:53.743
Alright, I'll go prepare the meal.

34:53.824 --> 34:55.304
The Yuzhen chicken here is good.

34:55.304 --> 34:57.024
You can eat
once you've finished talking.

35:04.864 --> 35:06.424
Don't tell anyone else she's here.

35:07.183 --> 35:07.984
Don't worry.

35:08.263 --> 35:10.984
When have I ever spoken of your things
to outsiders?

35:11.703 --> 35:12.504
Go on.

35:22.904 --> 35:24.464
What's with that look?

35:25.703 --> 35:28.663
Nothing. Have you found Master Zhu?

35:29.384 --> 35:32.824
I've searched all the inns, taverns,
and transport shops in the city.

35:33.384 --> 35:34.904
I haven't found any trace of him.

35:36.024 --> 35:39.143
Master Zhu said
he has a few old friends in the capital.

35:39.543 --> 35:42.824
Could he be staying
at someone's house as well?

35:42.824 --> 35:43.864
Did you go check?

35:44.223 --> 35:46.024
Sure, but I didn't find him.

35:47.063 --> 35:49.424
Li, when you fell off the cliff,

35:49.743 --> 35:51.263
are you sure you saw Master Zhu?

35:51.864 --> 35:53.063
Of course.

35:53.063 --> 35:54.663
Didn't I tell you last time?

35:57.504 --> 35:59.304
Where is Master Zhu hiding?

35:59.464 --> 36:02.223
It's very dangerous
for him to be outside alone.

36:02.703 --> 36:04.824
Don't worry. I'll keep looking.

36:05.183 --> 36:06.703
Don't worry about this matter.

36:07.663 --> 36:09.864
Well, you came here today,

36:10.223 --> 36:12.424
not just to ask about Master Zhu, right?

36:13.504 --> 36:14.824
I need your help.

36:14.904 --> 36:15.703
What is it?

36:16.904 --> 36:18.824
Mo Xiuyao agreed
to let me treat his legs.

36:18.904 --> 36:19.824
You must help me.

36:22.288 --> 36:26.768
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

36:28.864 --> 36:29.663
Master.

36:30.583 --> 36:31.784
Dowager Consort Qin is here.

36:34.464 --> 36:36.103
Got it. You may leave.

36:36.344 --> 36:37.024
Yes.

36:39.583 --> 36:40.944
Why have you come?

36:42.304 --> 36:46.103
What? Do you feel
that I made you lose face that day?

36:48.784 --> 36:49.583
I wouldn't dare.

36:51.063 --> 36:52.504
I was saving you.

36:55.504 --> 36:58.543
Zhou Jing, we've been friends
for many years.

36:58.703 --> 37:01.703
We've weathered storms together
and entrusted our lives to each other.

37:02.904 --> 37:06.583
I can turn a blind eye

37:06.784 --> 37:08.904
to what you've secretly been doing
for money.

37:09.143 --> 37:10.504
I can even exonerate you.

37:11.703 --> 37:13.143
But you must understand one thing.

37:13.344 --> 37:15.384
The reason we can stand together

37:15.583 --> 37:17.784
is that we are both
on the Empress Dowager's side.

37:19.183 --> 37:21.784
I have always remembered that.

37:22.784 --> 37:25.583
But what about the Empress Dowager?
Does she remember?

37:28.263 --> 37:33.183
The emperor, to seize real power,
has killed many of my people.

37:33.263 --> 37:34.904
Has the Empress Dowager seen this?

37:35.743 --> 37:39.143
Even a cripple like Mo Xiuyao
bossed me around.

37:39.743 --> 37:41.344
And how did the Empress Dowager respond?

37:43.384 --> 37:45.344
Not only did she not stand up for me,

37:45.583 --> 37:48.543
but she actually suspected me
because of Yuan Fang.

37:49.784 --> 37:51.944
Yuan Fang was her trusted confidant.

37:52.183 --> 37:53.864
He had never coveted power
before he died.

37:53.864 --> 37:55.904
He had been loyal
with absolute devotion.

37:55.944 --> 37:57.944
Why did you fight against a loyal man?

37:57.944 --> 37:59.263
I didn't.

37:59.904 --> 38:03.304
I only hope she won't pin the blame
for Yuan Fang's murder on me.

38:03.304 --> 38:03.944
Fine.

38:04.944 --> 38:07.864
Since you didn't kill him,
then find the real murderer.

38:08.543 --> 38:11.304
If you don't clear yourself
of suspicion,

38:11.583 --> 38:13.703
how can the Empress Dowager trust you
in the future?

38:13.784 --> 38:15.543
How can you hold onto your position?

38:15.543 --> 38:18.103
But those killed officials
were all loyal to me.

38:18.103 --> 38:20.944
Lu Changfu and his rats deserved to die.

38:21.464 --> 38:25.944
The pressing priority is
to regain the Empress Dowager's trust.

38:26.543 --> 38:29.864
With her trust,
you'll have a good future.

38:36.656 --> 38:38.608
(Pleasant and Calm)

38:48.904 --> 38:50.384
This is Master Yunqi.

38:50.703 --> 38:52.623
He is kind of a renowned physician
from Luoyang.

38:53.504 --> 38:56.784
He began studying medicine at seven
and has practiced for over 20 years.

38:57.024 --> 39:01.103
He is most skilled in orthopedics,
specializing in bone injuries.

39:03.344 --> 39:04.143
Thank you.

39:07.223 --> 39:09.703
Your Highness,
must the bones really be broken?

39:09.944 --> 39:11.944
It'll unavoidably injure his body.

39:16.304 --> 39:17.143
Don't worry.

39:17.703 --> 39:20.543
My technique can avoid further injury.

39:21.024 --> 39:22.944
I'll first use a fine needle
on the Qihai point.

39:23.143 --> 39:25.488
When breaking the bone,
it won't harm the blood vessels.

39:25.784 --> 39:29.464
But I'm not sure if Your Highness
can withstand this kind of pain.

39:30.223 --> 39:31.464
I'm not afraid of pain.

39:31.864 --> 39:36.183
I just don't know
if your technique is that good.

39:38.543 --> 39:42.304
I've merely read some old medical books
and lack experience.

39:42.743 --> 39:45.183
If I carelessly miss the acupoint,

39:46.263 --> 39:49.263
I can only beg for your forgiveness.

39:52.304 --> 39:53.984
You began studying medicine at seven.

39:54.904 --> 39:56.183
You should know

39:56.864 --> 39:59.784
that if the Qihai is injured,
it can cause lifelong paralysis.

40:00.824 --> 40:03.944
You won't ruin your own reputation,
will you?

40:06.344 --> 40:08.183
Master Yunqi just loves to joke.

40:08.904 --> 40:11.743
If we delay any longer,
the anesthetic's effect will wear off.

40:12.183 --> 40:13.223
Let's talk later.

40:15.312 --> 40:17.520
♪Why do you panic♪

40:18.416 --> 40:21.520
♪For no reason,
you pushed me away and left me♪

40:22.416 --> 40:25.200
♪Afraid we might start again♪

40:25.200 --> 40:29.330
♪Changing many things, right or wrong♪

40:29.776 --> 40:32.538
♪Fate is blurred and bewildering♪

40:33.328 --> 40:36.368
♪Are you also unwilling
to show weakness♪

40:37.136 --> 40:39.824
♪To recover what was once taken♪

40:40.176 --> 40:43.952
♪Our warmth will not be swallowed up♪

40:44.016 --> 40:46.928
♪Amidst life's ups and downs,
turns and twists♪

40:46.928 --> 40:50.777
♪Love has never strayed away♪

40:51.952 --> 40:53.680
♪Throughout this lifetime♪

40:53.680 --> 40:58.384
♪In the end, we're together again♪

40:58.608 --> 41:01.552
♪Countless trials and pleadings,
right or wrong♪

41:01.552 --> 41:05.987
♪Try to make this love quiet♪

41:06.896 --> 41:08.720
♪But we fight back♪

41:08.720 --> 41:15.536
♪To make it a tale to be told♪

41:15.824 --> 41:19.824
♪Deepest love is none other than♪

41:19.824 --> 41:21.680
♪Aligning my scars with yours♪

41:21.680 --> 41:23.291
♪What was once let go♪

41:23.291 --> 41:25.313
♪Will heal together from now on♪

41:25.313 --> 41:26.970
♪From your silhouette♪

41:26.970 --> 41:30.561
♪I see the same me♪

41:30.561 --> 41:33.904
♪If dreams become illusions♪

41:33.904 --> 41:36.560
♪With you I journey and find solace♪

41:36.560 --> 41:38.139
♪In the sole abode of heart♪

41:38.139 --> 41:40.128
♪We embrace and circle into a corner♪

41:40.128 --> 41:41.965
(Tuisi Pavilion)

41:41.965 --> 41:46.327
♪Love lightly brushes past♪

41:47.248 --> 41:49.260
♪Like you, like me♪

41:49.614 --> 41:52.208
♪The eyes are still clear♪

41:54.416 --> 41:56.506
♪None better than you,
and none better than me♪

41:57.104 --> 42:01.776
♪Love can last until the spring♪

42:03.312 --> 42:06.944
♪Silently, we turn pain into joy♪

42:06.944 --> 42:08.703
Don't chew. Hold it under your tongue.

42:09.143 --> 42:11.784
This is a pain relief pill.
It needs to dissolve in the saliva.

42:12.080 --> 42:15.664
♪So we can tightly fit together♪

42:15.664 --> 42:18.672
♪Without you, there's no me♪

42:18.960 --> 42:21.544
♪Passing by the world♪

42:21.544 --> 42:23.149
♪Part of my broken self♪

42:23.149 --> 42:25.240
♪Finds our places in an embrace♪

42:25.240 --> 42:26.896
♪Fulfilling our wishes♪

42:26.896 --> 42:31.184
♪Lovers remain calm and composed♪

42:32.140 --> 42:34.015
♪Like you, like me♪

42:35.944 --> 42:37.504
Are you feeling better now?

42:39.760 --> 42:42.032
♪None better than you,
and none better than me♪

42:42.032 --> 42:49.680
♪Love blooms at every spring and sunset♪

42:50.896 --> 42:53.648
(Preview)

42:54.223 --> 42:57.263
My parents used to call me Yao.

42:58.223 --> 43:00.063
Yao.

43:00.543 --> 43:03.263
I didn't expect you
to also be a master of Go.

43:04.143 --> 43:05.063
Again.

43:05.623 --> 43:07.944
I never imagined that you did that.

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
